{
  "text": "(WT, K119R/K120R, K125R/K128R/K130R and K119R/K120R/K125R/K128R/K130R) were established. FLAG-H2A was bound to anti-FLAG M2 resign under denaturing conditons (Sigma) as described previously [CITATION_1] . After elution with FLAG peptide the sample was separated via SDS PAGE and used for immunodetection. Pull down was checked by Coomassie staining.",
